00:05:52.778 --> 00:05:56.358
After leaving Western Union, Edison decided to devote

00:05:56.368 --> 00:05:59.918
himself entirely to his experiments and studies.

00:06:00.528 --> 00:06:07.038
In 1869, he obtained his very first patent and learned an invaluable lesson.

00:06:08.008 --> 00:06:13.458
Edison’s first patent was for his invention of the electric vote recorder.

00:06:14.138 --> 00:06:21.058
