You probably have a smartphone, you can send messages to anyone, anywhere, at any time.

00:08:38.168 --> 00:08:45.068
And not just text messages - you can send long text, pictures, video, audio.

00:08:45.278 --> 00:08:49.228
We can do anything, and indeed there are an estimated

00:08:49.238 --> 00:08:53.908
100 billion messages sent on WhatsApp every single day.

