But when Edison was growing up, sending just one series of beeps was complicated and expensive.

00:09:03.698 --> 00:09:09.168
And that was Edison’s opportunity, that was where there was money to be made.

00:09:09.998 --> 00:09:15.468
This first invention, the quadruplex telegraph, was important because it

00:09:15.498 --> 00:09:20.458
allowed telegraph companies to increase their efficiency and productivity.

