What Edison managed to do was turn invention into a career, turn

00:11:58.222 --> 00:12:04.122
the career of inventor into a glamorous and desirable one, and in so

00:12:04.122 --> 00:12:09.002
doing, turned himself into the country’s first celebrity inventor.

