00:19:42.949 --> 00:19:49.169
Edison believed that the simple act of falling asleep very briefly would revive him,

00:19:49.469 --> 00:19:55.129
allowing him to jump back into action, inspired and ready to start working again.

00:19:56.259 --> 00:20:03.009
Aside from doggedly working away at his inventions and seeking inspiration in strange ways,

00:20:03.379 --> 00:20:09.939
Edison also used all means available to ensure that his business ventures succeeded, including

00:20:10.189 --> 00:20:16.609
mergers, and taking a lot of legal action and when necessary discrediting his rivals.

00:20:17.547 --> 00:20:21.557
So, was Thomas Edison the greatest inventor in the world?

00:20:22.047 --> 00:20:24.367
He was certainly one of the most prolific.

00:20:24.947 --> 00:20:28.527
What’s more, he was also one of the most business-minded.

00:20:29.227 --> 00:20:33.307
Unlike many other inventors of his time, notably Nikola

00:20:33.307 --> 00:20:38.257
Tesla who died penniless and in debt, Edison died a rich man.

